      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Alex Morgan: Let\u2019s zoom out for a moment and frame sustainability as a systems question."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:8342c859d3813162",
      "properties": {
        "speaker": "Speaker 1",
        "text": "And I think the most useful way to approach this is to ask what must stay true over time."
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
